  "_notes": [
    "SYS1 = MESA Marion Co. Public Safety Simulcast, site hex A (decimal 10), NAC 261.",
    "shortName '10A' is the site identifier — NOT the P25 sysid (which is still 0x262=610).",
    "All four SYS1 CCs (856.1625, 856.5125, 857.6625, 858.1875 MHz) are within TRUNK0's range.",
    "SYS1 voice gap: 854.9875, 855.4875, 855.9875 MHz are below TRUNK0 and above TRUNK1 — missed.",
    "All other SYS1 voice (856.2–858.3 on TRUNK0, 858.8–860.0 on TRUNK2) is covered.",
    "Before starting in SYS1 mode, ensure config/talkgroups/10A.csv exists:",
    "  cp config/talkgroups/262.csv config/talkgroups/10A.csv",
    "To activate: set TR_CONFIG=trunk-recorder.sys1.json in .env, then:",
    "  docker compose up -d trunk-recorder",
    "To revert to SYS3: remove TR_CONFIG from .env (or set to trunk-recorder.json)."
